Types.title: Logging types
Types.description:
`messages` - Logs message events such as editing, deleting and pinning.
`channels` - Logs channel events such as creating, deleting and updating.
`users` - Logs user joining, leaving, banning, unbanning, and updating (kicked counts as leaving).
`roles` - Logs role creating, deleting and updating.
`scam` - Logs the suspected scams if the scam module is activated.
`all` - Logs everything onto that channel.

Invalid-type.title: Log
Invalid-type.description: Invalid type. Use `logs types` to see all types of logging.

MissingRequiredArgument.title: Error
MissingRequiredArgument.description: You are missing at least 1 required argument: `log <type> <channel>`

MissingPermissions.title: Error
MissingPermissions.description: You need `Administrator` permissions to set up logging.

Invalid-channel.title: Error
Invalid-channel.description: Invalid channel. Make sure it is an existent channel or that I can see it.
